{
  "_readme": [
    "Copy file ini ke settings.local.json (tanpa .example) dan sesuaikan dengan OS/setup kamu.",
    "File ini TIDAK git-ignored — aman untuk di-commit sebagai template.",
    "settings.local.json ADALAH git-ignored — jangan commit credentials atau path personal di sana.",
    "Pilih salah satu blok OS di bawah, hapus sisanya, lalu edit path sesuai mesin kamu."
  ],

  "_security_notes": [
    "JANGAN gunakan wildcard runtime: Bash(python3 *), Bash(node *), Bash(npm *), Bash(bun *)",
    "  → Wildcard tsb = arbitrary code execution (Claude bisa run file apa saja di sistem)",
    "GUNAKAN scope sempit: Bash(python3 ./**/*.py) = hanya file .py di project dir",
    "  → Bash(python3 -c ...) dan Bash(python3 /tmp/injected.py) akan diblokir",
    "Untuk tools tertentu, lebih aman gunakan module pattern: Bash(python3 -m pytest *)",
    "SELALU sertakan deny block: rm -rf dan sudo minimal"
  ],

  "_choose_your_os": "Hapus semua blok kecuali yang sesuai OS kamu, rename key jadi 'permissions'",

  "permissions_WINDOWS": {
    "allow": [
      "Read(./**)",
      "Read(~/.claude/**)",
      "Read(D:/Server/xampp/**)",
      "Read(D:/Server/laragon/**)",
      "Read(D:/Database/**)",

      "Bash(git *)",
      "Bash(php *)",
      "Bash(mysql *)",
      "Bash(composer *)",
      "Bash(sqlplus *)",
      "Bash(sqlplus.exe *)",
      "Bash(lsnrctl *)",
      "Bash(sc query *)",
      "Bash(net stop *)",
      "Bash(net start *)",

      "Bash(powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File *)",
      "Bash(bash -n ~/.claude/scripts/statusline.sh)",
      "Bash(chmod -R u+w .git/)",

      "Skill(update-config)",
      "Grep(**)",
      "Glob(**)",
      "Monitor(**)",

      "Write(./experiments/**)",
      "Write(./.claude/**)",
      "Edit(./.claude/**)",
      "Write(D:/Server/xampp/htdocs/**)",
      "Write(D:/Server/laragon/www/**)",
      "Edit(D:/Server/xampp/htdocs/**)",
      "Edit(D:/Server/laragon/www/**)"
